  </chunk>
  <chunk id="f6ed1f1e9999e57793addb1c9c54f61c7861a995.c3" text="Since TNF-α is pivotal in granuloma formation, the results indicated an unexpected positive function of MKP-1 against mycobacterial infection as opposed to its usual phosphatase activity.">
